---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Reveal } from '../components/Reveal';

const title = "Miro Kloosterman — Private retreats and integrated healing";
const description = "Private retreats, breathwork, bodywork, and integrated healing with Miro Kloosterman. Nine modalities, one practitioner, one room that feels safe.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center px-section-x py-24 overflow-hidden bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,_var(--color-primary-container)_0%,_var(--color-surface)_100%)]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 z-10">
        <Reveal client:load>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-soil-muted mb-8 block">Integrated Healing · Bali & Turkey</span>
          <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-display leading-[0.9] mb-12 text-soil">
            Some people say you never fully recover.
          </h1>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-8 mb-12">
            <div class="w-12 h-px bg-primary mt-4 flex-shrink-0"></div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display italic text-primary/80">
              I'm going to prove them wrong.
            </h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-soil-muted max-w-xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
            I'm Miro. I spent five years clawing my way out of Lyme disease, burnout, and grief — using every tool I could find. Nine of those tools became certifications. All of them became the work I do now, with people who are stuck in their body, their mind, or their life, and ready to find their way back.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
            <a href="https://tidycal.com/miro-kloosterman/15-minute-meeting" class="btn-primary">Book a discovery call</a>
            <a href="/about" class="btn-text">Read my story</a>
          </div>
        </Reveal>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative lg:translate-x-12">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-tactile rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700">
          <img 
            src="https://picsum.photos/seed/miro-hero/1200/1600" 
            alt="Miro Kloosterman" 
            class="object-cover w-full h-full scale-110 hover:scale-100 transition-transform duration-1000"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-12 -left-12 bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-xl shadow-tactile hidden lg:block max-w-xs">
          <p class="font-hand text-3xl text-primary mb-2">"The body remembers what the mind tries to forget."</p>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-soil-muted">Foundational Principle</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2 — Recognition -->
  <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-start">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display leading-tight text-soil">If you're here, something is asking for attention.</h2>
      </Reveal>
      <Reveal client:load delay={0.2}>
        <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-soil-muted">
          <p>Most people don't book a retreat because everything is fine. They book because something isn't moving, and they've tried the things that usually work, and those things aren't working this time.</p>
          <p>Maybe your body stopped cooperating and no bloodwork can tell you why. Maybe you've been running on willpower so long you forgot what rest feels like. Maybe grief is sitting in your chest and won't leave, even though your mind finished with it years ago. Maybe you've done yoga, therapy, breathwork, plant medicine — and something helped, but nothing moved the core thing.</p>
          
          <div class="therapy-note mt-12">
            <p class="text-xl text-soil font-medium italic mb-4">"None of this is a failure. It's information. It usually means the work you need now isn't one more modality on top of the others — it's someone who can read what your body is actually doing and meet it with the right tool at the right time."</p>
            <p class="font-hand text-3xl text-right text-primary">— Miro</p>
          </div>
          <p class="font-medium text-primary text-xl text-center pt-6">That's what I do.</p>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3 — The Work -->
  <section class="py-section-y px-section-x max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-24 max-w-4xl">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-primary mb-6 block">The Methodology</span>
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display mb-10 text-soil">Nine modalities. One practice. Integrated in real time.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-soil-muted leading-relaxed">
          Most practitioners specialise in one or two things. I integrate nine. Not as a menu to choose from—as a single practice I draw on depending on what the body in front of me actually needs.
        </p>
      </Reveal>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <Reveal client:load delay={0.1}>
        <div class="service-card h-full">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-display">Private Retreat in Bali</h3>
          <p class="text-soil-muted">Fully personalised. All-inclusive. Designed around what your body and your life actually need. This is the deepest work I offer.</p>
          <a href="/retreat" class="btn-text mt-auto w-fit">Explore the retreat</a>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
      <Reveal client:load delay={0.2}>
        <div class="service-card h-full lg:translate-y-12">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-display">Individual Sessions</h3>
          <p class="text-soil-muted">Breathwork, bodywork, water therapy, hypnotherapy, coaching. In-person by arrangement or online from anywhere.</p>
          <a href="/sessions" class="btn-text mt-auto w-fit">View sessions</a>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
      <Reveal client:load delay={0.3}>
        <div class="service-card h-full">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-display">Group Retreats</h3>
          <p class="text-soil-muted">Occasional immersive retreats co-facilitated with Damla Yaku. Bali, Turkey, and other destinations. Small groups. Real depth.</p>
          <a href="/group-retreats" class="btn-text mt-auto w-fit">See upcoming dates</a>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4 — The Pivot Story -->
  <section class="bg-primary text-on-primary py-section-y px-section-x overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-20 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1 relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-ambient -rotate-3">
          <img 
            src="https://picsum.photos/seed/miro-pivot/1000/1250" 
            alt="Miro's Transformation" 
            class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute top-12 -right-12 bg-secondary p-8 rounded-xl shadow-tactile hidden lg:block">
          <p class="text-on-secondary font-display text-2xl">From Dutch TV to<br/>Deep Healing</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2">
        <Reveal client:load>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display text-on-primary mb-12 leading-tight">Before this, I was on Dutch television.</h2>
          <div class="space-y-8 text-lg opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
            <p>You might know my face from Goede Tijden, Slechte Tijden. I played Thijs Kramer from 2014 to 2017, performed in The Bodyguard musical, appeared in The Passion, and later on the cover of Men's Health magazine.</p>
            <p>Between those chapters, my body stopped working.</p>
            <p>Childhood illness I'd been ignoring. Years of unhealthy habits. My mother died when I was two. My brother Goran died of cardiac arrest at thirty-three, while I was still contractually locked into the show. Then a relationship ended. Then burnout. Then Lyme disease, and five years of being told I might never fully recover.</p>
            <p>I left the show. I moved to Bali and began rebuilding from the foundation up — using the modalities I now offer to other people. Story magazine ran the full transformation in March this year.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-16 p-10 bg-surface-bright/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-on-primary/10">
            <p class="text-2xl font-display italic mb-6">"You can spend the rest of your life mourning, or you can decide to live."</p>
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest opacity-60">— Miro, Story Magazine, March 2026</p>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/about" class="btn-text text-on-primary mt-12 block w-fit">Read the full story</a>
        </Reveal>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5 — Reviews -->
  <section class="py-section-y px-section-x max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-24">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display mb-8 text-soil">The word people use first is safe.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto text-soil-muted leading-relaxed">
          In more than thirty reviews across every service I offer, one word shows up again and again—and it shows up before "transformation," before "healing," before anything else.
        </p>
      </Reveal>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-20">
      <Reveal client:load delay={0.1}>
        <div class="review-card h-full">
          <p class="text-xl italic text-soil-muted leading-relaxed">"What I experienced with Miro was beyond any description. Like I'm leaving my body and then coming back again but as a different person. It really feels like a rebirth."</p>
          <div class="mt-auto pt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-px bg-secondary"></div>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-soil">Christopher · Breathwork</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
      <Reveal client:load delay={0.2}>
        <div class="review-card h-full">
          <p class="text-xl italic text-soil-muted leading-relaxed">"After only one session, years of neck and shoulder tension was all gone. I finally feel like I can breathe again."</p>
          <div class="mt-auto pt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-px bg-secondary"></div>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-soil">Anna · Body Reset</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
      <Reveal client:load delay={0.3}>
        <div class="review-card h-full">
          <p class="text-xl italic text-soil-muted leading-relaxed">"I met many shamans, healers, coaches. He is the cleanest energy one. A true master of his craft."</p>
          <div class="mt-auto pt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-px bg-secondary"></div>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-soil">Dragonheart · Breathwork</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/reviews" class="btn-text">Read more reviews</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6 — Who This Is For -->
  <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-section-y px-section-x">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display mb-16 text-center text-soil">This is for you if…</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-10 mb-20">
          {[
            "You've been stuck for longer than you want to admit",
            "Your body is giving you signals and your doctor can't find anything",
            "You've tried a lot already — therapy, yoga, breathwork — and something knows there's still a layer underneath",
            "You're grieving something the rest of your life has finished with",
            "You want depth, not another modality to collect",
            "You want to do the real work, but only in a room that feels genuinely safe",
            "You're ready to travel to Bali or Turkey, or you're ready to start online from wherever you are"
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary"></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-lg text-soil-muted leading-snug">{item}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-12 md:p-16 rounded-xl shadow-tactile text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-2xl font-display italic mb-10 text-soil">"If you recognised yourself in more than a couple of those, the discovery call is the right next step. It's free. It's thirty minutes. No script, no pitch. Just a conversation about what's actually going on, and whether we're the right fit."</p>
          <a href="https://tidycal.com/miro-kloosterman/15-minute-meeting" class="btn-primary">Book a free discovery call</a>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 7 — Final Invitation -->
  <section class="py-section-y px-section-x text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <Reveal client:load>
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-display mb-12 text-soil leading-tight">Want to live your best life? I am here for you.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-soil-muted mb-16 leading-relaxed">
        The work I do is not for everyone. But if you're the person it's for, you probably already know. Reach out. Tell me what's going on. We'll figure out what to do next, together.
      </p>
      <div class="mb-16">
        <p class="text-soil-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">With Love,</p>
        <span class="font-hand text-6xl text-primary">— Miro</span>
      </div>
      <a href="https://tidycal.com/miro-kloosterman/15-minute-meeting" class="btn-primary">Book a free discovery call</a>
    </Reveal>
  </section>
</Layout>
